OL,6,FA letter Princess Diana wrote to an
OL,7,FAIDS victim in the 1990s is to be sold
OL,8,Fat auction in Cornwall.
OL,10,FIn the touching letter, written to
OL,11,FMichael Nanson in April 1994, Princess
OL,12,FDiana speaks of his "courage and quiet
OL,13,Fstrength" in coping with AIDS.
OL,15,FPrincess Diana was a global icon and
OL,16,Fused her fame to help others both
OL,17,Fpublicly and privately.
