OL,3,CThe letter Princess Diana wrote to
OL,4,CAIDS sufferer to boost his spirits
OL,6,FIn this private letter, she reached
OL,7,Fout to Michael - a young flight
OL,8,Fattendant who contracted AIDS in the
OL,9,Fearly 1990s. He died two months after
OL,10,Freceiving the letter.
OL,12,FIn the letter, she wrote the following:
OL,14,F"Dear Michael,
OL,16,F"Your sister had the very kind idea of
OL,17,Ftelling me about the courage and quiet
OL,18,Fstrength with which you are coping
OL,19,Fwith AIDS...
