OL,3,CThe letter Princess Diana wrote to
OL,4,CAIDS sufferer to boost his spirits
OL,6,F"I was so glad to hear from her
OL,7,Fbecause it has given me the chance to
OL,8,Fsend this brief note.
OL,10,F"Though inadequate, it comes with my
OL,11,Fthoughts and prayers - and the sure
OL,12,Fknowledge that your brave example will
OL,13,Fprove an inspiration to others.
OL,15,F"With love from,
OL,17,FPrincess Diana took a particular
OL,18,Finterest in HIV and AIDS and was
OL,19,Fpivotal in changing the public's
OL,20,Fperception of the disease back in the
OL,21,F1980s.
