OL,3,CThe letter Princess Diana wrote to
OL,4,CAIDS sufferer to boost his spirits
OL,6,FThe letter, along with a collection of
OL,7,Fcontemporary royal memorabilia, will
OL,8,Fgo on sale on Thursday 23 May at Lay's
OL,9,FAuctioneers in Lanner, Cornwall.
OL,11,FIt's being sold by Michael's family to
OL,12,Fmark 30 years since his death and the
OL,13,Ffamily plan to use the money to hold a
OL,14,Fsmall celebration to remember him.
